---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MoFa Agents - Moxin AI">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 text-accent-cyan text-sm font-bold mb-6">
        MoFa 框架
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight text-text-primary">
        让普通开发者成为 <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan to-blue-500">
          全栈 AI 工程师
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        通过连接专用代理构建复杂的代理工作流。从辩论到研究，MoFa 编排智能的流动。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 animate-fade-in">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan/10 to-blue-500/10 border border-accent-cyan/20 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all cursor-pointer text-center transform hover:scale-105" onclick="window.open('https://mofa.ai', '_blank')">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-text-primary">访问 MoFa 网站</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4 text-lg">探索 MoFa 代理框架的全部功能。</p>
        <span class="text-accent-cyan font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          mofa.ai 
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose MoFA -->
    <section class="mb-24 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-text-primary">为什么选择 MoFA</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">可组合代理架构</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">通过 YAML 定义的流程连接代理，构建复杂的 AI 应用。利用包含 RAG、规划和工具集成模块的核心内核。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">快速代理开发</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">清晰的代理开发结构，减少样板代码。MoFA Stage 可视化 IDE 加速从创建到调试的整个周期。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">丰富的代理中心</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">访问 100+ 预构建代理，涵盖数据连接器、LLM 集成和专用工具。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">高度可扩展</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">轻松编写自定义 Python 代理。通过定义良好的接口集成第三方工具、模型和数据源。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">MoFA Stage IDE</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">MoFA 的可视化管理平台 - 您的基于 Web 的 IDE。</p>
          <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm text-text-secondary">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              可视化代理管理
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              集成终端
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-cyan rounded-full"></span>
              Monaco 代码编辑器
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Real Examples -->
    <section class="mb-24 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-text-primary">真实案例：AI 数据流实战</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa/tree/main/examples/hello_world" target="_blank" class="group block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-cyan transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">Hello World</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">入门的基础代理示例。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa/tree/main/examples/arxiv_research" target="_blank" class="group block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-cyan transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">ArXiv 研究</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">自动化论文研究代理。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa/tree/main/examples/rag" target="_blank" class="group block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-cyan transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">RAG 系统</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">用于问答的检索增强生成。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa/tree/main/examples/gosim-pedia" target="_blank" class="group block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-cyan transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">GoSim 百科</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">多代理网络研究系统。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa/tree/main/examples/mem0-dataflow" target="_blank" class="group block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-cyan transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">Mem0 记忆系统</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">记忆增强的数据流。</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mofa-org/mofa/tree/main/examples/intelligent_agent_creation" target="_blank" class="group block bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-cyan transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-cyan transition-colors">代理创建系统</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">自动生成 AI 代理。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Started -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="animate-fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-text-primary">几秒钟内开始使用</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan shrink-0 font-bold">
              1
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary">安装 MoFA</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary">运行 pip 命令安装 MoFA 框架。</p>
              <code class="block mt-2 bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-sm text-text-secondary border border-gray-200">pip install mofa</code>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan shrink-0 font-bold">
              2
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary">创建您的代理</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary">使用我们的模板或从头开始使用简单的 YAML 配置。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-50 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan shrink-0 font-bold">
              3
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-text-primary">部署与扩展</h3>
              <p class="text-text-secondary">启动您的 AI 代理并在不同环境中扩展它们。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative animate-slide-up">
        <div class="relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl">
          <!-- Mock Flow Chart -->
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
            <div class="bg-cyan-50 border border-accent-cyan text-accent-cyan px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono font-bold shadow-sm">
              Manager Agent
            </div>
            <div class="h-8 w-px bg-gray-300"></div>
            <div class="flex gap-8">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-text-primary shadow-sm">
                  Researcher
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary text-center max-w-[150px]">
                  搜索网络获取最新数据
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-text-primary shadow-sm">
                  Writer
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary text-center max-w-[150px]">
                  根据研究起草内容
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-text-primary shadow-sm">
                  Critic
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary text-center max-w-[150px]">
                  审查并请求更改
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
